Commands_Description.Command: This is the command sent over the GPIB bus.
Commands_Description.Type: Whether or not it returns a value or just sets something.
Commands_Description.Argument: The parameter the command passes to the instrument. Optional parameters are denoted with an *. The types of paramters are int=integer, float=floating point number, string=string, and None=NULL.
Commands_Description.Returns: What gets returned by the function.
Commands_Description.Description: A one line describing the purpose of the function, for more detailed info look in the manual.
